_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Overthrown.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403193504\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.042 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.065 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1014/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8943/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3928/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2341/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 5634/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   53.579      1 -total\n 55.60%   29.791      2 Template:Date\n 36.67%   19.645     11 Template:Ref\n 22.44%   12.022     11 Template:Ref/core\n  6.01%    3.218      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:16059-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403193504 and revision id 290680\n -->\n",
